Single Reference Image Processing:

Copy the path of your images folder.

* on RunPod always add "/" before workspace path.

Input image Size should match Empty Latent size.

Use Image Crop Node to adjust your input image.

This is a node by King Cashflow
It allows you to replace key character features from Florence 2 captions with your custom ai character features.

Example:

image_style: facebook photo of, amateur photography, cinematic shot etc...

Gender_age_replacement: middle aged woman, young woman, young man, 25yo woman with dark hair and large breasts.

lora_trigger: if you have a lora connected to the workflow, you can add trigger words here.

Negative_prompt: works only on saved output.txt file.


Output.txt file can be loaded using:
1 - Load Prompts from File (Inspire-Pack)
2 - Unzip Prompt (Inspire-pack)
